import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import App from './App'
import 'antd/dist/antd.css'
import reportWebVitals from './reportWebVitals'
import {
  HashRouter as Router
} from 'react-router-dom'

ReactDOM.render(
    <Router>
      <App/>
    </Router>,
  document.getElementById('root')
)

reportWebVitals()
